{"questionId":"13810047","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The cost of a journey on the different boat routes is given in the following table; all prices are given in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>USD</mi></math>. The cost of a journey is the same in either direction between two ports.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/f8c5fd340751d010c11ffcea6632ac8f6a9ba4a5.png\"></p>\n<p>Sofia wants to make a trip where she travels on each of the boat routes at least once, beginning and ending at port <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Draw graph <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>G</mi></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><img src=\"__IMG__/0c62ee2cd6bd0089a864885dbff62e31a3409580.png\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"13810047","referenceCode":"23N.2.AHL.TZ0.5a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Draw graph G.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","AHL 3.14—Graph theory","Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","AHL 3.15—Adjacency matrices and tables"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":3}
